name: Mynock
Lore: 'Silicon-based space borne lifeform. Frequently called a ''power sucker.'' Feeds on energy such as stellar radiation and electrical discharges. Absorbs minerals from starship hulks.',
Text: 'Habitat: unlimited. Parasite: Starfighter. Host''s power and hyperspeed are cumulatively -2; while both < 1, Mynocks randomly detach one at a time (cannot attach for remainder of turn). Moves like a starfighter.',
